## ğŸ”§ Technical Details

- **New Function**: `Get-ZurgTotalTorrentStats`
- **API Calls**: +1 per check (to `/manage/`)
- **Performance**: <1 second added
- **Breaking Changes**: None

---

## âš¡ Performance Impact

```
v2.1: 2 API calls per check (~2 seconds)
v2.2: 3 API calls per check (~3 seconds)

Impact: Minimal - barely noticeable
```

---

## ğŸ¨ Color Guide

- **White**: Total torrent count
- **Green**: OK torrents (healthy)
- **Yellow**: Broken (if any)
- **Cyan**: Under repair (if any)
- **Gray**: Zero count (none found)

